\ldblquote I\rquote m sure Professor Dumbledore will tell you. \'85 Now, behave, won\rquote t you? \i Won\rquote t\i0  you, Fred? And you, George?\rdblquote\par
The pistons hissed loudly and the train began to move.\par
\ldblquote Tell us what\rquote s happening at Hogwarts!\rdblquote  Fred bellowed out of the window as Mrs. Weasley, Bill, and Charlie sped away from them. \ldblquote What rules are they changing?\rdblquote\par
