Harry, Ron, and Hermione went back to their compartment. The thick rain splattering the windows made it very difficult to see out of them. Ron undid his trunk, pulled out his maroon dress robes, and flung them over Pigwidgeon\rquote s cage to muffle his hooting.\par
\ldblquote Bagman wanted to tell us what\rquote s happening at Hogwarts,\rdblquote  he said grumpily, sitting down next to Harry. \ldblquote At the World Cup, remember? But my own mother won\rquote t say. Wonder what \emdash\rdblquote\par
