\ldblquote It\rquote s bewitched,\rdblquote  said Hermione. \ldblquote If a Muggle looks at it, all they see is a moldering old ruin with a sign over the entrance saying DANGER, DO NOT ENTER, UNSAFE.\rdblquote\par
