A gleeful smile spread across Malfoy\rquote s pale face.\par
\ldblquote Don\rquote t tell me you don\rquote t \i know\i0 ?\rdblquote  he said delightedly. \ldblquote You\rquote ve got a father and brother at the Ministry and you don\rquote t even \i know\i0 ? My God, \i my\i0  father told me about it ages ago \'85 heard it from Cor\-nelius Fudge. But then, Father\rquote s always associated with the top peo\-ple at the Ministry. \'85 Maybe your father\rquote s too junior to know about it, Weasley \'85 yes \'85 they probably don\rquote t talk about impor\-tant stuff in front of him. \'85\rdblquote\par
Laughing once more, Malfoy beckoned to Crabbe and Goyle, and the three of them disappeared.\par
Ron got to his feet and slammed the sliding compartment door so hard behind them that the glass shattered.\par
\ldblquote\i Ron\i0 !\rdblquote  said Hermione reproachfully, and she pulled out her wand, muttered \ldblquote\i Reparo\i0 !\rdblquote  and the glass shards flew back into a sin\-gle pane and back into the door.\par
