\ldblquote You are preoccupied, my dear,\rdblquote  she said mournfully to Harry. \ldblquote My inner eye sees past your brave face to the troubled soul within. And I regret to say that your worries are not baseless. I see difficult times ahead for you, alas \'85 most difficult \'85 I fear the thing you dread will indeed come to pass \'85 and perhaps sooner than you think. \'85\rdblquote\par
