\ldblquote What?\rdblquote  said Ron shortly.\par
\ldblquote Your dad\rquote s in the paper, Weasley!\rdblquote  said Malfoy, brandishing a copy of the \i Daily Prophet\i0  and speaking very loudly, so that every\-one in the packed entrance hall could hear. \ldblquote Listen to this!\par
\par
