Harry and Hermione both laughed, and Hermione began dol\-ing beef casserole onto each of their plates.\par
\ldblquote He could have really hurt Malfoy, though,\rdblquote  she said. \ldblquote It was good, really, that Professor McGonagall stopped it \emdash\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Hermione!\rdblquote  said Ron furiously, his eyes snapping open again, \ldblquote you\rquote re ruining the best moment of my life!\rdblquote\par
Hermione made an impatient noise and began to eat at top speed again.\par
\ldblquote Don\rquote t tell me you\rquote re going back to the library this evening?\rdblquote  said Harry, watching her.\par
\ldblquote Got to,\rdblquote  said Hermione thickly. \ldblquote Loads to do.\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote But you told us Professor Vector \emdash\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote It\rquote s not schoolwork,\rdblquote  she said. Within five minutes, she had cleared her plate and departed. No sooner had she gone than her seat was taken by Fred Weasley.\par
\ldblquote Moody!\rdblquote  he said. \ldblquote How cool is he?\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Beyond cool,\rdblquote  said George, sitting down opposite Fred.\par
\ldblquote Supercool,\rdblquote  said the twins\rquote  best friend, Lee Jordan, sliding into the seat beside George. \ldblquote We had him this afternoon,\rdblquote  he told Harry and Ron.\par
