Was anyone except Ron and Hermione going to believe him, or would they all think he\rquote d put himself in for the tournament? Yet how could anyone think that, when he was facing competitors who\rquote d had three years\rquote  more magical education than he had \emdash  when he was now facing tasks that not only sounded very danger\-ous, but which were to be performed in front of hundreds of peo\-ple? Yes, he\rquote d thought about it \'85 he\rquote d fantasized about it \'85 but it had been a joke, really, an idle sort of dream \'85 he\rquote d never really, \i seriously\i0  considered entering. \'85\par
