\ldblquote Yeah, give Ron a good kick up the \emdash\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote\i Write to Sirius.\i0  You\rquote ve got to tell him what\rquote s happened. He asked you to keep him posted on everything that\rquote s going on at Hogwarts. \'85 It\rquote s almost as if he expected something like this to happen. I brought some parchment and a quill out with me \emdash\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Come off it,\rdblquote  said Harry, looking around to check that they couldn\rquote t be overheard, but the grounds were quite deserted. \ldblquote He came back to the country just because my scar twinged. He\rquote ll prob\-ably come bursting right into the castle if I tell him someone\rquote s en\-tered me in the Triwizard Tournament \emdash\rdblquote\par
