\ldblquote Okay, okay, I\rquote ll write to him,\rdblquote  said Harry, throwing his last piece of toast into the lake. They both stood and watched it floating there for a moment, before a large tentacle rose out of the water and scooped it beneath the surface. Then they returned to the castle.\par
