\ldblquote That was a very decent thing you just did, Potter,\rdblquote  Moody said quietly.\par
Harry didn\rquote t know what to say; this wasn\rquote t the reaction he had expected at all.\par
\ldblquote Sit down,\rdblquote  said Moody, and Harry sat, looking around.\par
