\ldblquote What? Oh not at all, not at all!\rdblquote  said Bagman. \ldblquote No, they were just telling me a bit more about those fake wands of theirs. Won\-dering if I could advise them on the marketing. I\rquote ve promised to put them in touch with a couple of contacts of mine at Zonko\rquote s Joke Shop. \'85\rdblquote\par
