\ldblquote Eh?\rdblquote  said Hagrid blankly. \ldblquote No, don\rquote  go! I\rquote ve \emdash  I\rquote ve never met another one before!\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Anuzzer \i what,\i0  precisely?\rdblquote  said Madame Maxime, her tone icy.\par
