\ldblquote Another half-giant, o\rquote  course!\rdblquote  said Hagrid.\par
\ldblquote  \rquote Ow dare you!\rdblquote  shrieked Madame Maxime. Her voice exploded through the peaceful night air like a foghorn; behind him, Harry heard Fleur and Roger fall out of their rosebush. \ldblquote I \rquote ave nevair been more insulted in my life! \rquote Alf-giant? \i Moi\i0 ? I \rquote ave \emdash  I \rquote ave big bones!\rdblquote\par
