\ldblquote So?\rdblquote  Harry prompted Ron. \ldblquote What\rquote s the problem with giants?\rdblquote\par
\ldblquote Well, they\rquote re \'85 they\rquote re \'85\rdblquote  Ron struggled for words. \ldblquote\'85 not very nice,\rdblquote  he finished lamely.\par
