\ldblquote Well \'85 no one who knows him will care, \rquote cos they\rquote ll know he\rquote s not dangerous,\rdblquote  said Ron slowly. \ldblquote But \'85 Harry, they\rquote re just vicious, giants. It\rquote s like Hagrid said, it\rquote s in their natures, they\rquote re like trolls \'85 they just like killing, everyone knows that. There aren\rquote t any left in Britain now, though.\rdblquote\par
