Ron mouthed soundlessly like a goldfish out of water as Hermione turned on her heel and stormed up the girls\rquote  staircase to bed. Ron turned to look at Harry.\par
\ldblquote Well,\rdblquote  he sputtered, looking thunderstruck, \ldblquote well \emdash  that just proves \emdash  completely missed the point \emdash\rdblquote\par
Harry didn\rquote t say anything. He liked being back on speaking terms with Ron too much to speak his mind right now \emdash  but he somehow thought that Hermione had gotten the point much bet\-ter than Ron had.\par
