\ldblquote There\rquote s still the fact that Dumbledore trusts Snape, and I know Dumbledore trusts where a lot of other people wouldn\rquote t, but I just can\rquote t see him letting Snape teach at Hogwarts if he\rquote d ever worked for Voldemort.\rdblquote\par
