\ldblquote Yes, he\rquote s quoted in the article in there,\rdblquote  said Sirius, nodding at the paper. \ldblquote Blustering on about how bad Bertha\rquote s memory is. Well, maybe she\rquote s changed since I knew her, but the Bertha I knew wasn\rquote t forgetful at all \emdash  quite the reverse. She was a bit dim, but she had an excellent memory for gossip. It used to get her into a lot of trou\-ble; she never knew when to keep her mouth shut. I can see her being a bit of a liability at the Ministry of Magic \'85 maybe that\rquote s why Bagman didn\rquote t bother to look for her for so long. \'85\rdblquote\par
Sirius heaved an enormous sigh and rubbed his shadowed eyes.\par
\ldblquote What\rquote s the time?\rdblquote\par
